{"tid":1124644,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個世界真係好多癡線既人","createTime":"2019-04-25T07:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T07:11:50.000Z","uid":250440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d03fc1b262f6be88ed3f8cabfd477241a9c183f","tid":1124644,"uid":250440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:09:59.000Z","msg":"［借ac］<br />\n<br />\n今日真係激撚氣！<br />\n鑒於以前去麥當勞有好多次叫走冰冇走冰既經驗<br />\n我習慣會搖一搖隻杯睇下係咪真。走冰<br />\n咁我今日攞餐個陣都搖咗搖<br />\n排後面個嗰呀嬸冇啦啦開始發癲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀女你唔可以咁做架<br />\n咁我初頭以為佢講電話冇理佢<br />\n佢重複多次我先知佢講緊我<br />\n我咪聽下我做錯D咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />xxxxx (聽唔清佢噙咩)有冇人教過你架？你要唔要睇下你爸爸係唔係假架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吓？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(對住個店員講)快D叫經理出嚟！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？？？？？我做錯左D咩？我做錯D咩你講呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(五出聲眼超超)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我摸到隻杯有D凍搖一搖隻杯睇下有冇走冰有錯咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我做錯咗咩啫？我將杯野撥落你度定點呀下？我做錯咗d咩！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫經理出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我黎m睇下有冇走冰都做錯咗咩？？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哦，甘叫埋醫院<br />\n<br />\n個下我覺得佢係癡線，唔想理佢就走咗<br />\n但之後好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解我冇好好甘屌佢！！<br />\n股氣積係心好躁，胃口都冇曬<br />\n我成世人做錯過好多野，都未撚試過咁撚無辜俾人鬧<br />\n大家鬧下佢安慰下我"},{"pid":"ea5193acba547d908f1fd34bcaf5fbd77e3eff46","tid":1124644,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:11:31.000Z","msg":"甘你老母"},{"pid":"12611608042c635b228e77e08df971df5761cd17","tid":1124644,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:11:36.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1bfde7c8f2f19d251440beb91774bea1e0061f1","tid":1124644,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:11:50.000Z","msg":"點解要同痴線計較<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人地有白卡嘅話 你就唔夠人玩"}]}